---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import WWFProgrammesCarousel from '../components/WWFProgrammesCarousel.jsx';
import InteractiveMission from '../components/InteractiveMission.jsx';
---

<LandingLayout title="About WWF North Africa">
  <!-- Enhanced header with clear navigation showing where user is in the journey -->
  <header class="w-full p-4 border-b border-neutral-200 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <!-- Logo and brand -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/course_website/academy-logo.jpg" alt="WWF Academy Logo" class="h-8"/>
        <span class="font-bold text-neutral-700">WWF North Africa</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation with breadcrumb-style indication -->
      <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-6">
        <a
          href="/course_website/"
          class="text-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-900 font-medium transition-colors"
        >
          ← Home
        </a>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-semibold border-b-2 border-blue-900 pb-1">
          About WWF
        </span>
        <a
          href="/course_website/chapter1/"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-900 text-white rounded-md font-bold text-sm hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
        >
          Start Course →
        </a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Mobile navigation -->
      <div class="md:hidden">
        <a
          href="/course_website/chapter1/"
          class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-900 text-white rounded text-sm font-bold"
        >
          Start Course
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section with enhanced messaging about the learning journey -->
    <section class="py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg-alt) 100%);">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <!-- Breadcrumb indicator for learning journey -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-600 bg-blue-50 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="mr-2">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
            Step 1 of your learning journey
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6"
          style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary); letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
        >
          About WWF North Africa
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed"
          style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-text-muted);"
        >
          Understanding our mission, conservation programs, and the critical environmental challenges
          facing North Africa will provide essential context for your upcoming course journey.
        </p>

        <!-- Enhanced CTA section with learning path guidance -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="#programmes"
            class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-300 border"
            style="
              background-color: var(--color-primary);
              color: white;
              border-color: var(--color-primary);
              font-family: var(--font-sans);
            "
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-accent)'; this.style.borderColor='var(--color-accent)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-primary)'; this.style.borderColor='var(--color-primary)'"
          >
            Explore Our Programmes
          </a>
          <a
            href="/course_website/chapter1/"
            class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-300 border"
            style="
              background-color: var(--color-bg);
              color: var(--color-primary);
              border-color: var(--color-primary);
              font-family: var(--font-sans);
            "
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-bg-alt)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-bg)'"
          >
            Ready for Course? Start Learning →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Progress indicator showing where they are in the learning journey -->
        <div class="mt-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-2">
            <span>Learn About WWF</span>
            <span>Start Course</span>
            <span>Complete Training</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-neutral-200 rounded-full h-2">
            <div class="bg-blue-900 h-2 rounded-full w-1/3"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Interactive Mission Statement (includes impact statistics) -->
    <InteractiveMission client:load />

    <!-- Programmes Carousel Section with enhanced educational context -->
    <section id="programmes" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <!-- Section introduction to connect programs with course content -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-12">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4"
          style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary);"
        >
          Our Seven Conservation Programmes
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-lg leading-relaxed"
          style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-text-muted);"
        >
          These real-world conservation initiatives provide the practical foundation for the theoretical
          concepts you'll encounter in our course. Each programme addresses specific challenges that
          you'll study in detail through our curriculum.
        </p>
      </div>

      <WWFProgrammesCarousel client:load />

      <!-- Bridge to course content -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mt-12">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4"
            style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary);"
          >
            Ready to Dive Deeper?
          </h3>
          <p
            class="text-lg mb-6"
            style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: var(--color-text-muted);"
          >
            Now that you understand our conservation mission and programmes, you're ready to explore
            the scientific principles and methodologies that guide our work. Our comprehensive course
            will teach you the ecosystem science behind these conservation efforts.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/course_website/chapter1/"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-blue-900 text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          >
            Begin Your Scientific Journey
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="ml-2">
              <path d="M7 17l9.2-9.2M17 17V7H7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action with enhanced course transition -->
    <section class="py-16" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6"
          style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: white;"
        >
          Transform Knowledge Into Action
        </h2>
        <p
          class="text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed"
          style="font-family: var(--font-sans); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);"
        >
          Our conservation programmes demonstrate what's possible when scientific knowledge meets
          practical action. Through our course, you'll develop the expertise to contribute to these
          vital conservation efforts and create positive environmental impact across North Africa.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <!-- Primary action: Start the course -->
          <a
            href="/course_website/chapter1/"
            class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-300 border"
            style="
              background-color: white;
              color: var(--color-primary);
              border-color: white;
              font-family: var(--font-sans);
            "
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--color-bg-alt)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='white'"
          >
            Start Learning Now
          </a>

          <!-- Secondary action: Get more info -->
          <a
            href="/course_website/resources/"
            class="px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-300 border"
            style="
              background-color: transparent;
              color: white;
              border-color: white;
              font-family: var(--font-sans);
            "
            onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)'"
            onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'"
          >
            View Course Resources
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Learning path reminder -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-white/80">
            <strong>Next:</strong> Chapter 1 - Global Ecosystem Principles
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</LandingLayout>